      (Birabuto Kingdom) [Remix]\n\n<b><color=red>Tater-Tot Tunes</color></b>\nStage
      Boss (8-BIT) - Super Mario 64\nBuoy Base Galaxy - Super Mario Galaxy\n\n<b><color=red>TheLegendofRenegade</color></b>\nNew
      Super Mario Bros. - Walking The Hot Desert (Sega Genesis Remix)\nNew Super
