      Bros.\nSuper Mario Bros.\nSuper Mario Bros. 3\nSuper Mario World\nSuper Mario
      Sunshine\nNew Super Mario Bros.\nMario Kart Wii\nMario Kart 8\nMario Party
      4\nSuper Mario Party\nMario & Luigi: Bowser's Inside Story\nSuper Mario Maker
      2\nSuper Smash Bros. Ultimate\n\n<b><color=red>Pozosta\u0142\u0119</color></b>\nBaldi's
      Basics\nMinecraft\nSonic the Hedgehog\n\n<b><color=yellow>Shadery</color></b>\n\nScrolling
      Sprite - ewersp na GitHub\nUnity Standalone File Browser - gkngkc na GitHub\nNative
