      Emulator - PixelSagas\nSuper Mario Bros. 3 - Nintendo\nNineteen Eighty Seven
      - Chequered Ink\nSuper Mario Maker 2 - SonicFontsHD\nSuper Mario Maker Extended
      - Dale Thiessen\n\n\n\n<b><color=blue>Podzi\u0119kowania specjalne</color></b>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<sprite
